	<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE="margin-right: 0cm; background: transparent; line-height: 150%; page-break-before: always">
	<IMG SRC="/images/TpRkUjVMbhc/27900a1b.png" ALIGN=BOTTOM WIDTH=551 HEIGHT=782 BORDER=0></P>
	<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE="margin-right: 0cm; background: #ffffff; line-height: 150%">
	- форма платежных средств
	(табл. 9.3.)</P>
	<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE="margin-right: 0cm; background: transparent; line-height: 150%">
	
